  "prompt": "How many credits are on Quora?",
  "response": "Quora used to use a system of credits, which allowed users to ask questions and promote content, but as of mid-2021, Quora phased out the credits system. Users no longer earn or spend credits on the platform, as Quora shifted its focus towards other ways to engage and support content creators, such as its Partner Program or subscriptions to Spaces. Therefore, currently, there are no credits on Quora.",
